description:
Get a unique entertainment experience and enjoy your favorites movies and TV Shows, find all genres from Action and War to Romance and Comedy and much more.

The app will help you to find the right movie for you using smart features and intelligent recommendations, you can also watch the movie trailer with an exceptional experience of the Augmented Reality.

FEATURES:

- Clean UI that will help you find your movies easily.
- Movies are structured into well refined categories (Popular, Trending ...)
- Get notifications and stay updated with the movie you love.
- Advanced & smart search (Find movies, shows, actors ...).
- Get movies details, trailers, cast, similar & recommendations.
- The app learns while you use it so you will get customized recommendations for you.
- You can watch all movies trailers normally or using the Augmented Reality technology.

- This app is not for streaming/watching movies.
- All movies/shows information and images/data are from TMDB.org API licensed under CC BY-NC 4.0: (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/) and according to their terms of use: (https://www.themoviedb.org/documentation/api/terms-of-use).

Inkitt da vida a las historias
Únete a Inkitt y sé parte de la comunidad
Sumérgete en Inkitt, donde las historias, los libros y las novelas cobran vida en una comunidad global de lectores y escritores. Nuestros lectores marcan tendencia. Cada día, millones de personas visitan Inkitt para descubrir el próximo best-seller. Recibe retroalimentación sobre tu trabajo, comparte tus historias favoritas de romance o aventura y explora un tesoro de novelas de fantasía y erotismo.

Lectura ilimitada, una biblioteca de novelas independientes te espera
Disfruta de lectura ilimitada en tus géneros favoritos. Ya sea romance apasionante, aventuras emocionantes, fantasía cautivadora o erotismo provocativo, aquí hay algo para todos:

Descubre novelas independientes de escritores prometedores
Explora nuevas temáticas como romances de la mafia, aventuras de fantasía o tu fanfiction erótica favorita
Descarga libros para leer sin conexión en cualquier momento
Personaliza tu experiencia con fuentes y colores ajustables
Activa el desplazamiento automático y sumérgete por completo en tus historias favoritas
Conviértete en el próximo éxito literario
Inkitt es la primera editorial del mundo impulsada por los lectores, conectando a los lectores con nuevos libros, novelas cautivadoras e historias extraordinarias. Nuestra plataforma alberga joyas de romance, aventura y fantasía que esperan ser descubiertas. Los autores independientes que brillan pueden obtener oportunidades de publicación o adaptación, haciendo que sus libros lleguen a fans en todo el mundo.

Best-sellers globales en Inkitt
Keily de Manjari
Beautiful Mistake de Mel Ryle
Colt de Simone Elise
Yes, Mr. Knight de Natalie Roche
Hated by My Mate de Nathalie Hooker
The Millennium Wolves de Sapir Englard
When the Night Falls de Nureyluna
The Lycan’s Queen de LS Patel
Mason de Zainab Sambo
The Arrangement de SS Sahoo
Apoya a tus autores favoritos
A través de nuestro Programa de Suscripción para Autores, los lectores pueden apoyar directamente a escritores independientes. ¿Te encantan sus historias? Suscríbete para ayudar a que sus novelas sigan vivas y creciendo.

¿Quieres unirte a la comunidad?
Síguenos en redes sociales y conversa con los autores de Inkitt en Discord.

Presentamos la nueva WebNovel: ¡tu puerta de entrada a emocionantes aventuras! Sumérgete en un mundo de novelas cautivadoras y embárcate en viajes inolvidables. Estamos aquí para redefinir la forma en que experimenta la lectura en línea: leamos sus aventuras.

Descubre un tesoro escondido de géneros novedosos que te transportarán a reinos más allá de tu imaginación. Sumérgete en las maravillas de la fantasía occidental, donde deambulan criaturas míticas y se desarrollan misiones épicas. Disfrute del encanto de la fantasía oriental, con fascinantes historias de wuxia, xianxia, xuanhuan y más. Piérdete en el encanto de las novelas fantásticas que te mantendrán hechizado de principio a fin.
Pero eso no es todo: tenemos algo especial para los fanáticos de las novelas de sistema, los litRPG y la fantasía de progresión. Experimenta la emoción de subir de nivel y desbloquear nuevos poderes junto a tus personajes favoritos mientras navegan por mundos inmersivos similares a los de un juego.

Con WebNovel, tienes acceso a una vasta biblioteca de novelas cautivadoras, escritas por autores talentosos de todo el mundo. Nuestra interfaz intuitiva garantiza una experiencia de lectura perfecta, permitiéndole sumergirse por completo en cada giro y giro.

Comience su viaje de lectura hoy con WebNovel, donde cada página es una invitación a escapar de la realidad y embarcarse en misiones extraordinarias. ¡Prepárate para leer tus aventuras como nunca antes!

Géneros destacados: Misterio, Fantasía oriental, Fantasía occidental, Ciencia ficción, Fan-fic, Xianxia, Xuanhuan, Wuxia, Romance, Mangas de aventuras, Cómics, Manhua, Webtoon
Novelas Originales y Exclusivas: Mago Supremo, Mi sistema vampírico. Esclavo de las sombras
Novelas traducidas y exclusivas: Biblioteca del camino al cielo, El señor de los misterios, Ella se vuelve glamorosa después de la anulación del compromiso
Cómic exclusivo/Manga/Manhua/Manhwa/Webtoon: La Bella y la Bestia, Cuando la Bella se encuentra con las Bestias

Únase a miles de aspirantes a autores. Comience su viaje contando sus historias en WebNovel. "El viaje de mil millas comienza con un solo paso". Únase a nuestro concurso quincenal de sugerencias de escritura y publique su novela con nuestro sistema de emparejamiento para millones de lectores que comparten un interés similar en su género. Encuentra tu voz y comparte tu mensaje con el mundo.

Muchos géneros de libros te esperan para explorar en la aplicación WebNovel.

Cualquiera puede encontrar sus novelas cómicas/manga/manhua/fanfic/webtoon favoritas en WebNovel. ¡Empiece a leer historias sin demora!

A PLAY Games é uma publicação mensal que concentra - há mais de dez anos - as maiores novidades, lançamentos, análises, dicas e curiosidades deste segmento. Sua especialidade são detonados, roteiros completos e minuciosos dos jogos mais populares da geração PlayStation.

Faça o download grátis da PLAY Games e compre edições avulsas ou assine diretamente do seu iPad, iPhone ou iPod Touch. 

• Assinatura auto-renovável PlayStation - Revista Oficial 

• Duração da assinatura e quantidade de edições enviadas durante a assinatura: 
• Assinatura de 1 ano (1 year subscription) – 12 edições 
• Assinatura de 6 meses (6 months subscription) – 6 edições 
• Assinatura de 1 mês (1 month subscription) – 1 edição 

• Preço da assinatura auto-renovável e edições avulsas: 
• Assinatura de 1 ano - Preço: US$ 30.99 (automaticamente renovada até que seja cancelada) 
• Assinatura de 6 meses - Preço: US$ 15.99 (automaticamente renovada até que seja cancelada) 
• Assinatura de 1 mês - Preço: US$ 2.99 (automaticamente renovada até que seja cancelada) 
• Edição avulsa – Preço: US$ 2.99 

• O pagamento será debitado da sua conta do iTunes no momento da confirmação da compra 

• A assinatura é renovada automaticamente a menos que a renovação automática seja cancelada pelo menos 24 horas antes do final do período vigente 

• A renovação da sua assinatura será cobrada no prazo de 24 horas antes do final do período vigente e identificada o custo da renovação 

• As assinaturas podem ser gerenciados pelo usuário e a auto-renovação pode ser cancelada. Isso pode ser feito nas configurações da conta do usuário após a compra 

• Nenhum cancelamento da assinatura atual é permitida durante o período de assinatura vigente 

• Por favor, encontre nossos Termos e Condições e Política de Privacidade em: http://www.europanet.com.br/privacidade/ios/ 


Caso você seja assinante da revista impressa, basta entrar no app com seu e-mail e código de assinante para acessar suas revistas digitais gratuitamente. 

Qualquer dúvida, entre em contato com a nosso suporte técnico pelo e-mail: suportedigital@europanet.com.br

Listen AI: Desvelando el Poder del Texto a Voz

Convierte texto en voz y escucha todo lo que lees.

Listen AI no es solo una herramienta de texto a voz; es tu compañero ideal para acceder a la información narrada a tu ritmo. Descubre cómo Listen AI transforma tu experiencia:

Voces Impresionantes: Escucha narraciones claras y expresivas que suenan naturales. Escoge entre varios acentos y estilos para cualquier tipo de contenido.
Personalización Completa: Ajusta la velocidad de lectura y el volumen según tus preferencias.
Integración Sin Esfuerzo: Convierte texto de documentos, páginas web y PDFs en contenido hablado sin necesidad de copiar y pegar.
Multitarea con Estilo: Aprende mientras cocinas, haces ejercicio o viajas. ¡Escucha mientras haces más!
Accesibilidad para Todos: Ideal para personas con discapacidades visuales o dificultades de aprendizaje. Transformamos texto en experiencias de audio atractivas.

Listen AI: Más que leer, es vivirlo.

Términos y Condiciones: https://static.listenai.app/terms-conditions-en.html
Política de Privacidad: https://static.listenai.app/privacy-en.html
Normas de la Comunidad: https://static.listenai.app/community-guidelines-en.html

HappyMood – Discover Games Made for You

Are you a true gamer looking for one place to explore everything about games? HappyMoods is your ultimate companion! With a huge database of games, you can easily search, discover, and enjoy all the details you need in one simple app.
Explore a Massive Library HappyMood Browse through a wide range of games across different styles and categories. Whether you love action, adventure, puzzle, or strategy, HappyMods brings everything together in one place.
Watch Trailers & Gameplay Before playing, get a real taste of the game! Watch trailers and gameplay videos to see exactly what the game looks like.
Save Your Favorites HappyMood Build your own personalized collection of favorite games. Add the ones you love and come back to them anytime.
Track Games You Like Never lose track of a game again. Follow the games you’re interested in and keep them organized in your list.
Choose Your Mood Not sure what to play? Select your mood and HappyMod will recommend games that match how you feel at that moment. Fun, relaxing, scary, or exciting – there’s always a game waiting for you.
Test Your Knowledge Think you know everything about games? Try our quiz and challenge yourself with fun questions to see how much of a gaming expert you are.
All-in-One Gaming Experience HappyMood makes it easy for you to discover new games, keep track of your favorites, enjoy videos, and even test your knowledge. It’s everything a gamer needs – simple, clear, and always fun.
With HappyMod, finding the perfect game has never been easier.

Got a growing TBR list? See great book recommendations, but forget them later? Meet TBR Bookshelf!

Easily track books you want to read, are currently reading, or have finished with no limits. Rate and review books once you’ve read them and log your favorite moments using our quick and intuitive rating system. Browse public ratings to see a book’s POV, tropes, reread rate, and up to four genre-specific ratings. For example, Romance tracks Spice, Fluff, Humor, and Tear. All ratings are anonymous, so you can be honest with your reviews.

Within our rating system, you can log:
* Reading format
* 5 Star Rating including half stars
* Up to four genre ratings
* If you would reread a book
* DNF (Did Not Finish)
* Favorite characters and quotes
* Series and standalone books
* Pro quotes and annotations (Paid Subscription Required)
* Any additional thoughts about the book
Celebrate your reading milestones with special book confetti and earn stickers for completing books and certain book tropes.
Exclusive Pro features include:
* Book tropes
* Book playlists to track songs (cannot be played within the app)
* POV format and amount
* TV show and movie adaptation ratings
* Four seasonal ratings
All users can create custom yearly reading goals. When you finish a book, it is automatically added to your yearly reading goal bookshelf. Pro users can also fully customize their bookshelves with color themes, bookshelf items, and layouts.

TBR Bookshelf makes managing your TBR list fun, easy, and satisfying. Track books, set reading goals, log quotes, and discover new reads all in one place. With customizable shelves, anonymous ratings, and a supportive community, staying on top of your reading has never been more enjoyable.

Join TBR Bookshelf, a woman-owned and operated company, BookTok’s favorite, and trusted by millions of readers.

Listening is more ENJOYABLE and PRODUCTIVE than reading.
Text To Speech: Audio Books is an AI technology that enables to convert and read aloud any text as speech imitative of the human voice. This app transforms text, books, document, PDF and online articles into audiobooks. Now you can stay informed while cooking, driving, work out, doing sports, commute and let Text To Speech work as a text reader for you.

Text To Speech - Audiobooks is an essential tool for all kinds of reader, especially for those who are busy and want to enjoy audiobooks or people with dyslexia and other reading difficulties. The app is like an audible book, it can read aloud any text, webpages, PDF, eBooks or text book to you with our high quality natural sounding voices.

FEATURE LIST:
• Listen to articles, PDF, digital text, or physical books AS AUDIO.
• Listen with 50+ high quality natural human voices and 20+ languages.
• Listen at any speed you like, even faster or slower 5x than usual speed.
• Scan physical book pages with your device camera and convert to audible text.
• Import internet articles and online news straight from your mobile browser.
• Upload and convert photo, PDF and Docs file from iCloud, Google Drive, Dropbox.
• Listen to audible text with your iOS iPhone and iPad
• Organize listening files with library
• Support multiple languages: English, Spanish, German, French, Portuguese, Japanese, Italian, Russian, Dutch, Finnish, Swedish, Danish, Turkish, Polish, Hungarian, Vietnamese, Arabic, Hindi, Korean, Thai.


I. LISTEN TO ANY TEXT - IN ANYWHERE - AT ANYTIME:
Import PDF, photo of physical book pages, document, online articles, web pages or insert clipboard-copied text and let Text To Speech read aloud text to you in the natural human voice. Don't read anymore! Let's listen to your text!

II. +50 VOICES FOR BOTH MAN AND WOMEN, SUPPORTED 20 LANGUAGES:
Text To Speech provides more 50 high quality human voice across 20 languages. Just pick your favourite voice and find the perfect reading speed that works for you.

III. READ FASTER, REMEMBER LONGER
Text To Speech helps highlight each word as it reads. Listening and reading at the same time can maximize the levels of comprehension and help the reader remember longer than usual.

IV. SOLUTION FOR USERS WITH READING DYSLEXIA:
Text To Speech is a perfect solution for users with Dyslexia, ADHD, Low vision acuity, anxiety, concussions, and other reading disabilities to breeze through their readings and engage with their curiosities.


With Text To Speech : Audio Books, you can save time, retain more information, and stay focused. No matter what kind of reader you are, experience more with Text To Speech - Natural Reader.
